Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱美拉情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有吃貓糧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總感覺它有什麼地方不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶它去醫院比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說怎麼看都是吃太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然六花說著什麼「巨大化計劃」 餵了它很多貓糧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她還在睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒的時刻已然到來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 光之使者會將我灼燒至盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 我需要黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你灼燒至盡到你高興為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:58.31,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wanna fallin' LOVE.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.98,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}予感--… 夢が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.83,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}約束しても　心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.93,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ひとりじゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.68,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}信じたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:32.39,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思い続けてる だけで幸せなんて言えないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:38.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虚ろな自信背負っていても　君が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:44.32,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そして私の勇気になる 一つの言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.92,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君の世界を変えられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:51.45,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二つの恋が進化する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:55.67,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ホントだよ　巡らせた迷いが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.02,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見つけた答えは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.90,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつでも君に導かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:05.43,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}届ける覚悟が 様にならなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:08.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}素直に伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.84,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ココロアルガママコエガキラメク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:12.12,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Real come on voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.63,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響き渡るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.98,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}預感--… 夢想延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.83,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管許下約定 心中某處依舊膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.93,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.68,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}明明想要這樣相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:32.39,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思念不斷滋生 但是卻無法說出幸福二字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:38.19,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}雖背負著虛無的自信 你依然嘴角上揚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:44.32,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的一句話就能成為我的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.92,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}若能改變你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:51.45,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就能進化成為兩份愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:55.67,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}真的哦 冥思苦想依舊迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.02,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}最終找到的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.90,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}無論何時都能引領著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:05.43,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就算沒有做好能夠傳達給你的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:08.19,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}大聲地說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.84,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}心靈深處的聲音熠熠生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.63,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響亮地傳達給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了呢 第二學期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(247,318)\3c&H000000&\fs29}Last Episode  黃昏的…高級契約
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(369,288)\3c&H000000&\fs21}Higher Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話 雖然是和我一起離開的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她說她要先走 一個人跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Bonjour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：法語，你好。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Ciao
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：意大利語，你好。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長假過得如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,438)\fs21}Long Vacationg
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺丹生谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次一到新學期就會變得奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期也請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吐槽了呢 丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森大人還是一如既往的有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我只對茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只對茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對茴香學姐是很專一的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 暑假前可沒這麼高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你變矮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盯著什麼看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假才剛剛結束 就連話也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對六花露出一副渴求的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你們…分手了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的時候 兩人之間吹起了秋風…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說正好相反啊相反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 終於有了夏季的初體…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傷害了主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！話說你是從哪裏冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你也在聽啊 話說你又變成原樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 沒什麼好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從統計上來看高二的夏天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是…是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總歸只是統計而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那個話題已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是從今早開始六花就有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是你對主人的態度很過分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 富堅君又跟七宮關係很好地聊天之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 那麼簡單的事情也是會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說六花每天都去找她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事情以後她們兩個人的關係挺好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅君想在你的耳邊低語他的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 確實有點怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 換誰都會逃跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸吧 現充
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 你給我回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該回去的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有說什麼奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是和她一起尋找天使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓暗炎龍復活 所以會去幫他的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說過她在想要不要和勇者定下高級契約
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經把暗炎龍復活了 她說作為契約者這是必須的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學和小鳥游同學締結的好像是戀人契約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個高級契約就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼臉紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做下流的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你在說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉紅的不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一年級卻懂這種下流的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我才沒有想這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守什麼都沒有想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是說謊 你想像了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游同學把衣服脫掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說啊 別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是接吻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱美拉如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和早上差不多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.88,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親吻 男孩子的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的話就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學不來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因為有女生之間的對話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是傳說中的妖精之泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會有什麼樣的精靈住在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會又想多管什麼閒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小鳥游同學 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有必要特地來浴池嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學也不可能來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游同學也逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她想攻擊我也沒有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨蛋也跟來了 是我的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凸守 來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有個很有趣的浴池哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是音場型的修行之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我冥想結束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也正好 趁現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游同學 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我正在集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為必定會到來的時刻做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定會到來的時刻是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更高級的契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會被丹生谷你讀透我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乃森夏的神技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(469,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆戰錘使也要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(366,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想殺了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 經由喚醒暗炎龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為契約者的他應該得到了鞏固
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 一切還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制我的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解出這個問題就給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為給我黑色的東西就能讓我言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡亂對待作為契約者的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙以為隨便說點黑暗什麼什麼的就能哄我開心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人發狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那樣就可以締結高級契約了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 繼續這樣下去肯定不會有任何變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚回了暗炎龍的現在 應當締結與之相應的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越去想身體越像要溶解了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我對各位有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位看住我不要讓我繼續逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被表白了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我有在做游泳池的放哨人這份工作對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字好像叫做千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這不是在自誇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對茴香學姐是很專一的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我才在暑假一直打工想準備一個禮物給她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠同學 我很想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…叫他千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠同學 居然能在這種地方遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們肯定是被命運的紅線牽在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色 祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後你還是沒弄明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這一次小鳥游同學口風特別嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想自己說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說希望你放學後到這個地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好地讓她說明白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點就很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得小森大人還真是非常喜歡大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(467,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆戰錘使 時間快到了 得趕緊躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(256,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼主人 祝武運昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 果然我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是邪王真眼拜託我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看住你不要讓你繼續逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼戀人契約的高級契約種類也不是只限於這一種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種契約也只是像完成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這種時候逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止也都是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰勝了恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與勇者邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入勇者的懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與勇者締結契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為邪王真眼是最強的才做到了這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有邪王真眼才能走到今天這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就相信它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:13:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是最強的哦 邪王真眼和她的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我所有的魔力都傳給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在磨蹭些什麼啊 富堅他快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說我們也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼 一切都是連關天則
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 又發現什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 格爾松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(441,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我締結邪王真眼戀人契約的高級契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼說了你還是不明白我的意思的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經陳述完我的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通世界的借口對於邪王真眼來說只是細枝末節
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底締結還是不締結 你選！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的 這是個錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我逃走 請抓住我的雙肩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 剛才有一個什麼黑暗之物附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 我想接近勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明想呆在勇太的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻害羞…害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼我會這樣害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才這樣說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要勉強自己做出改變 那樣是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我是永遠的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以索菲亞將一切都交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須讓交給我的這份感情開花結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦 雖然我想理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我果然還是根本不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過你居然考慮得那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花你 以前也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起度過愉快的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回到共同的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這更幸福的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在同一個屋檐之下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回來 一起吃飯 一起打遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時而憤怒 時而歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會覺得麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一件件的小事 就是所謂的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其緊緊相擁 與其擁吻對方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何像戀人的事情都要更加地…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在更近的距離感覺到六花的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天長地久 我只會注視著你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 雖然是一點點地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實在變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年之前 我們還做不到這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始只是勾住手指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來牽住了手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是一點點地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實在變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 凱美拉它？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 它生孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 趕緊回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 家人要增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱美拉二號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是二號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連七號都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合成獸軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們該不會打算就這樣結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們要生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們原來在的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊做吧 我們可是一直在照顧你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一點點給我們看看也沒什麼的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是「趕緊做」什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用這麼下流的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這以後會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花的中二病會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我和六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會像至今為止所想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始一直以來所想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來也一直這樣互相思念下去吧
